-# A compact done/not-done list of training or exercise items for the student
-# overview. Each row is a status pill plus the item name (linked to its
-# Dashboard page when a URL is available). Local: `items` (StudentStatusContext
-# ItemRow list — name, done, url).
%ul.lti-overview-list
  - items.each do |item|
    %li.lti-overview-item
      %span.lti-status{ class: item.done ? 'lti-status--done' : 'lti-status--pending' }
        = item.done ? t('lti.assignment_view.status.completed') : t('lti.assignment_view.status.not_started')
      - if item.url
        = link_to item.name, item.url, target: '_blank', rel: 'noopener'
      - else
        = item.name
